From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Your Name <you@example.com>
Date: Mon, 24 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix deprecated wasm32-wasi target

Clang deprecated --target=wasm32-wasi in favor of --target=wasm32-wasip1.
This patch updates the build system to use the new target name.

---
 build/moz.configure/toolchain.configure | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/build/moz.configure/toolchain.configure b/build/moz.configure/toolchain.configure
index abcdef1..1234567 100644
--- a/build/moz.configure/toolchain.configure
+++ b/build/moz.configure/toolchain.configure
@@ -1119,7 +1119,7 @@ def c_compiler_wrapper(host_or_target, ccache, wrapper):
 
 @dependable
 def wasm():
-    return split_triplet("wasm32-wasi", allow_wasi=True)
+    return split_triplet("wasm32-wasip1", allow_wasi=True)
 
 
 @template
-- 
